    q: "Should I hire a freelancer or an agency?",
    a: "It depends on your budget and the complexity of your project. Freelancers are a solid choice for simpler sites with a tighter budget. Agencies are better suited for larger projects that need a team, a defined process, and ongoing support after launch."
